|  Rule   |       Connotation        |                            Elucidation                             | Example |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|suffix ? |    boolean as output     |                Is or not is. the output is boolean.                |  空? 𥥪?  |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|suffix ! |    same as usage of 攵    |Means directly modify the original data instead of creating new one,| 􏿰􏾘! 􏿰𠛮! |
|         |                          |                      thus the output is void.                      |         |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|suffix ~ |          softly          |         Immediately returns result once meet the request.          |  􏹊~ 􏹇~  |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|suffix ^ |      list as input       |                   The type of input data is list                   |  􏹊^ 伄^  |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|suffix + |same type objects as input|             "more than one same type objects as input"             | 􏿰攸+ 􏿰􏾩+ |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|include /|            Of            |               output is determinated by prefix of /                |􏿴/组合 􏿴/分组|
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

